One agent solution: ```Note that $(\mathbf{u} \times \mathbf{v}) \cdot \mathbf{w} = \mathbf{u} \cdot (\mathbf{v} \times \mathbf{w}).$

Since $\mathbf{u}$ and $\mathbf{v}$ are unit vectors,
